HEADWORD: Gemul
<hw>Ge*mul"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A
small South American deer (<spn>Furcifer Chilensis</spn>), with simple
forked horns.</def> <altsp>[Written also <asp>guemul</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
